      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Our replicated means match the paper exactly. Notice that by Wave 2, the average\n",
        "starting wage in NJ jumped to \\$5.08 (just above the new \\$5.05 minimum), while PA\n",
        "wages barely moved. This confirms the policy was binding in NJ.\n",
        "\n",
        "### Table 3 — Difference-in-Differences (Rows 1–3, Columns i–iii)\n",
        "\n",
        "This is the heart of the paper. We compare average FTE employment before and after\n",
        "the minimum wage increase in NJ vs. PA."
      ],
      "id": "e3c12aac"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "#| label: table3\n",
        "\n",
        "nj_fte1 = NJ['FTE'].mean()\n",
        "pa_fte1 = PA['FTE'].mean()\n",
        "nj_se1  = NJ['FTE'].sem()\n",
        "pa_se1  = PA['FTE'].sem()\n",
        "\n",
        "nj_fte2 = NJ['FTE2'].mean()\n",
        "pa_fte2 = PA['FTE2'].mean()\n",
        "nj_se2  = NJ['FTE2'].sem()\n",
        "pa_se2  = PA['FTE2'].sem()\n",
        "\n",
        "diff1    = nj_fte1 - pa_fte1\n",
        "diff2    = nj_fte2 - pa_fte2\n",
        "nj_chg   = nj_fte2 - nj_fte1\n",
        "pa_chg   = pa_fte2 - pa_fte1\n",
        "did      = nj_chg - pa_chg\n",
        "\n",
        "# SE for diff-in-diff (independent samples approximation)\n",
        "se_diff1 = np.sqrt(nj_se1**2 + pa_se1**2)\n",
        "se_diff2 = np.sqrt(nj_se2**2 + pa_se2**2)\n",
        "se_chg_nj = np.sqrt(nj_se1**2 + nj_se2**2)\n",
        "se_chg_pa = np.sqrt(pa_se1**2 + pa_se2**2)\n",
        "se_did   = np.sqrt(se_chg_nj**2 + se_chg_pa**2)\n",
        "t_did    = did / se_did\n",
        "\n",
        "results = {\n",
        "    \"\": [\"PA (i)\", \"NJ (ii)\", \"NJ – PA (iii)\", \"Paper DiD\"],\n",
        "    \"Row 1: FTE before\":  [f\"{pa_fte1:.2f}\", f\"{nj_fte1:.2f}\", f\"{diff1:.2f}\", \"–2.89\"],\n",
        "    \"Row 2: FTE after\":   [f\"{pa_fte2:.2f}\", f\"{nj_fte2:.2f}\", f\"{diff2:.2f}\", \"–0.14\"],\n",
        "    \"Row 3: Change\":      [f\"{pa_chg:.2f}\", f\"{nj_chg:.2f}\",\n",
        "                           f\"{did:.2f}\\n(t={t_did:.2f})\", \"2.76\\n(t=2.03)\"],\n",
        "}\n",
        "print(pd.DataFrame(results).to_string(index=False))"
      ],
      "id": "table3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
